title: Tulsa Race Massacre - What Happened?!
description:
Hi Friends!
Hope you have been staying happy and healthy out there, big hugs all around. Today I wanted to talk about the Tulsa Race Mass. Sad sad story and it was just the 101 year anniversary !
Love and appreciate you guys so much and I will be seeing you very soon.
x o
Bailey Sarian
